text: Piroska Csontos (born 11 February 1994) is a Hungarian Paralympic athlete who competes in sprinting and long jump events in international level events. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:People from Kiskunfélegyháza Category:Paralympic athletes of Hungary Category:Hungarian female sprinters Category:Hungarian female long jumpers Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Paralympics
title: Piroska Csontos
